# Role-Based Access Control — Admin & User

## Arsitektur Role
Aplikasi memiliki 2 role utama:
- `admin` — akses penuh ke semua halaman + Master Data Management
- `user` — akses terbatas ke halaman operasional pribadi

---

## Struktur Halaman

```
pages/
├── shared/          # Publik, tidak perlu auth
│   ├── Login
│   ├── ForgotPassword
│   └── ResetPassword
├── admin/           # Role: admin only
│   ├── Dashboard
│   ├── Attendance
│   ├── Leave
│   ├── Notification
│   ├── Offsite
│   ├── Overtime
│   ├── Permission
│   ├── Permit
│   ├── Profile
│   ├── Update
│   ├── WorkFromHome
│   └── MasterDataManagement   # HANYA admin
└── user/            # Role: user only
    ├── Dashboard
    ├── Attendance
    ├── Leave
    ├── Notification
    ├── Offsite
    ├── Overtime
    ├── Permission
    ├── Permit
    ├── Profile
    ├── Update
    └── WorkFromHome
```

