## Implementasi Laravel Filament v3

### 1. Model User — Role Attribute
```php
// app/Models/User.php
use Illuminate\Database\Eloquent\Casts\Attribute;

protected function casts(): array
{
    return [
        'role' => RoleEnum::class, // 'admin' | 'user'
    ];
}

public function isAdmin(): bool
{
    return $this->role === RoleEnum::Admin;
}

public function isUser(): bool
{
    return $this->role === RoleEnum::User;
}
```

### 2. Enum Role
```php
// app/Enums/RoleEnum.php
<?php
namespace App\Enums;

enum RoleEnum: string
{
    case Admin = 'admin';
    case User  = 'user';
}
```

### 3. Panel Separation — Filament
```php
// app/Providers/Filament/AdminPanelProvider.php
->authGuard('web')
->authMiddleware([Authenticate::class])
->login(CustomLogin::class)
->path('admin')

// app/Providers/Filament/UserPanelProvider.php
->authGuard('web')
->authMiddleware([Authenticate::class])
->login(CustomLogin::class)
->path('portal')
```

### 4. Redirect Setelah Login Berdasarkan Role
```php
// app/Filament/Pages/Auth/CustomLogin.php
protected function getCredentialsFromFormData(array $data): array
{
    return [
        'email'    => $data['email'],
        'password' => $data['password'],
    ];
}

public function authenticate(): ?LoginResponse
{
    $response = parent::authenticate();
    $user = auth()->user();

    return $user->isAdmin()
        ? redirect('/admin/dashboard')
        : redirect('/portal/dashboard');
}
```

### 5. Middleware Role Guard
```php
// app/Http/Middleware/EnsureRole.php
public function handle(Request $request, Closure $next, string $role): Response
{
    if (!auth()->check() || auth()->user()->role->value !== $role) {
        abort(403, 'Akses ditolak.');
    }
    return $next($request);
}
```

### 6. Policy — Contoh untuk Approval
```php
// app/Policies/LeavePolicy.php
public function viewAny(User $user): bool
{
    return true; // semua bisa lihat
}

public function approve(User $user): bool
{
    return $user->isAdmin(); // hanya admin
}

public function create(User $user): bool
{
    return $user->isUser(); // hanya user biasa
}
```

### 7. Filament Resource — Batasi Akses
```php
// Setiap Resource admin
public static function canAccess(): bool
{
    return auth()->user()->isAdmin();
}

// Master Data — hanya admin
public static function canAccess(): bool
{
    return auth()->user()?->role === RoleEnum::Admin;
}
```

