## Testing Checklist

- [ ] Login admin → redirect ke `/admin/dashboard`
- [ ] Login user → redirect ke `/portal/dashboard`
- [ ] User akses `/admin/*` → 403 Forbidden
- [ ] Admin lihat semua data karyawan di halaman Attendance
- [ ] User hanya lihat data absensi milik sendiri
- [ ] User tidak melihat menu Master Data Management
- [ ] Admin bisa approve/reject Leave, Overtime, WFH, Offsite, Permission, Permit
- [ ] User tidak bisa akses tombol approve/reject
